{"tid":470934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"直認缺乏性生活 母雞慘遭巴基斯坦少年性侵致死！！！！","createTime":"2017-11-16T19:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T09:18:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":72,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"35c1f1a2737d708d6839d2710e03da9ab215ed2f","tid":470934,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T19:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/022613_0007b6787aea2be5c5cd8568afccec4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F022613_0007b6787aea2be5c5cd8568afccec4d.jpg&h=612190b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n11月16日(四) 23:02   <br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦賈巴爾普爾14歲少年侯賽因（Ansar Hussain），上周六（11日）從鄰居店中偷來一隻母雞，然後將其性侵致死。警方以「不正常罪犯行為」將他拘捕。少年將性侵一事直認不諱，又指自己「缺乏性生活，才會偷母雞強暴」。 <br />\n<br />\n侯賽因從鄰居阿里（Mansab Ali）的商店偷走母雞後，直接帶回家性侵。兩名鄰居發現，趕緊報警處理。母雞承受不了摧殘，氣絕身亡。專家確認母雞遭性侵後，加上目擊者的供詞，警方隨即逮捕侯賽因。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171116/mobile/bknint-20171116230251180-1116_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171116%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20171116230251180-1116_17011_001.html&d=rMV4%2BPA%2FG49xNX6m63avINibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=19c5643e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171116/mobile/bknint-20171116230251180-1116_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"63c088b48f03fb79afe0d29a49ade0a51ccb9e8d","tid":470934,"uid":12564,"like":224,"dislike":1,"score":223,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T19:33:44.000Z","msg":"想偷我雞？.jpg"},{"pid":"4658aab8ba9a5085d8991ee8e646da0006505458","tid":470934,"uid":17231,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T19:39:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想偷我雞？.jpg</blockquote><br />\n有聲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1a36d6e8575cf208684333a6367d8fb349e3c6","tid":470934,"uid":25148,"like":248,"dislike":0,"score":248,"citedBy":0,